{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"08c46e5d13","title":"致华东局等电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"81088c48d7","index":0,"year":1949,"month":6,"day":14,"articleId":"08c46e5d13"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji26","name":"毛泽东全集第26卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji26.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji26":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"6310903304","type":"paragraph","text":"致华东局等电！","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji26","articleId":"08c46e5d13"},{"id":"797f96b452","type":"paragraph","text":"（1949年6月14日）驻福州附近的国民党军第十七集团军侯镜如部参课处长来港接治。据称，十七集团军辖有七十三军、七十四军、一〇六军，已疏通到可无问题之地步。但因势单力薄，难于主动起义，希望和我们前线取得联系配合此事请你们通知叶飞、谭震林及福建省委引起极大注意，不要放弃一切可能性争取供镜如各军反正。除由香港方面努力策动外，请你们即速研究与侯镜如取得联系的办法[1]这是毛泽东为中共中央军委起草的致华东局，票裕、张震、周骏鸣","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji26","articleId":"08c46e5d13"}],"page":{"id":"53b0ea66e1","publicationId":"maoquanji26","articleId":"08c46e5d13","start":472,"end":472}}}},"__N_SSG":true}